different decisions

00:52:28.240 --> 00:52:29.590
before it actually came out.

00:52:29.590 --> 00:52:31.120
And by measuring the difference
between that prediction

00:52:31.120 --> 00:52:33.036
and the actual outcome,
that's one of the ways

00:52:33.036 --> 00:52:34.800
that we can determine
our efficacy.

